<li>Translator for the Italian full collection of the 12 issues of the SI: <i><a href="http://www.ecn.org/nautilus/intersituaz.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ecn.org/nautilus/intersituaz.html" rel="nofollow">Internazionale situazionista 1958-69</a></i>, Publisher: Nautilus, Turin, 1994. The volume contains the following introduction by Lippolis:
<ul>
<li>( February 1993 ) <i><a href="http://www.ecn.org/nautilus/is58doc.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ecn.org/nautilus/is58doc.html" rel="nofollow">L’Internazionale sconosciuta Contributo all’aborto di una familiarità fittizia</a></i></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Daniele_Luttazzi" title="Daniele Luttazzi">Luttazzi, D.</a> (2008) <i><a href="http://www.danieleluttazzi.it/node/371" class="external text" title="http://www.danieleluttazzi.it/node/371" rel="nofollow">Pesci selvatici e le melodie delle foreste andaluse</a></i> December 2008 <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(Italian)</span></li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Tom_McDonough&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Tom McDonough (page does not exist)">McDonough, T.</a> (2002) <i><a href="http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1248/is_7_90/ai_88582347/pg_1" class="external text" title="http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1248/is_7_90/ai_88582347/pg_1" rel="nofollow">Art in America</a></i> July 2002</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Mustapha_Khayati&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Mustapha Khayati (page does not exist)">Khayati, M.</a> (1966), <i>On the Poverty of Student Life Considered in its Economic, Political, Psychological, Sexual, and Especially Intellectual Aspects, with a Modest Proposal for Doing Away With It</i>, from <a href="http://www.cddc.vt.edu/sionline/si/poverty.html" class="external text" title="http://www.cddc.vt.edu/sionline/si/poverty.html" rel="nofollow">Situationist International Online</a>, also available at <a href="http://library.nothingness.org/articles/SI/en/display/4" class="external text" title="http://library.nothingness.org/articles/SI/en/display/4" rel="nofollow">nothingness.org</a>.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Francesco_Poli" title="Francesco Poli">Poli, F.</a> (1991), <i>Sulla scia dei surrealisti</i>, published in <i>I Situazionisti e la loro storia</i> (p. 63). <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(Italian)</span></li>
</ul>
